contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the id of the pricebook for the product in transaction.
contextAttributes.title: Pricebook

contextAttributes.description: This Tag represents the Id of the Price Adjustment Schedule which has the volume based adjustments configured for the line item/ product in the transaction.
contextAttributes.title: PriceAdjustmentSchedule

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the type of header discount being applied to the transaction , where it is of type Percentage amount or override.
contextAttributes.title: HeaderDiscountType

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the value of header discount being applied to the transaction , for a given discount type.
contextAttributes.title: HeaderDiscountValue

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the logic used to spread the header discount across line items , whether it is spread equally or proportionally.
contextAttributes.title: HeaderDistributionLogic

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the type of header discount distribution or spread, whether is spread on net unit price or on line item total.
contextAttributes.title: HeaderDistributionType

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the quantity of the line item/ product in the transaction.
contextAttributes.title: Quantity

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the effective from date for the lone item to be considered for contract based pricing.
contextAttributes.title: StartDate

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the count or number of pricing terms associated with the item, displayed as a numeric value.
contextAttributes.title: PricingTermCount

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the unit price of the item in the transaction, displayed in the currency format.
contextAttributes.title: UnitPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the id of the product to be priced in the transaction , this is at a line item level.
contextAttributes.title: Product

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the list price value fetched from the pricebook for the lineitem/ product in the transaction.
contextAttributes.title: ListPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the value of the line item’s net total price.
contextAttributes.title: NetTotalPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the id of the ProductSelling Model (like one time , recurring etc) for the product in the transaction.
contextAttributes.title: ProductSellingModel

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the term or duration of the subscription for the item, displayed as a numeric value.
contextAttributes.title: SubscriptionTerm

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents what is the selling model type of a product, values can be One time or recurring or term defined.
contextAttributes.title: SellingModelType

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents whether or not a line item has contract based price , this is a boolean value.
contextAttributes.title: IsContracted

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the Price Adjustment schedule Id which has the volume adjustments to be applied under Contract.
contextAttributes.title: ContractVolumePasId

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the Contract Price Adjustment schedule to be considered when applying contract based product attribute discounts
contextAttributes.title: ContractAttributePasId

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the contractual discount type (like percentage) to be applied on list price of a product
contextAttributes.title: ContractDiscountType

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the contractual discount value of a given type to be applied on list price of a product
contextAttributes.title: ContractDiscountValue

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the contract based price of a product , this can be a flat override price or a price arrived at after applying the contracted discount.
contextAttributes.title: ContractPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the floor price or the minimum price allowed for a line item by business, so as to prevent over discounting and loss of margins.
contextAttributes.title: MinimumNetUnitPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the group or category to which the sales transaction item belongs.
contextAttributes.title: SalesTransactionItemGroup

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the last lowest price recorded for the line item for the duration of price tracking enabled.
contextAttributes.title: ItemRecordedPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the the net price per unit of the lineitem.
contextAttributes.title: NetUnitPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the total amount for the line item in the transaction, displayed in the currency format.
contextAttributes.title: TotalLineAmount

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the main or primary product associated with the bundle ,displayed as text.
contextAttributes.title: MainItemProduct

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the selling model or strategy associated with the bundle, displayed as text.
contextAttributes.title: MainItemProductSellingModel

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the root product or base product associated when a line item is a bundle.
contextAttributes.title: RootItemProduct

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the selling model or strategy associated with the root product of a bundle, displayed as text.Examples are One time , Recurring.
contextAttributes.title: RootItemProductSellingModel

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents whether the bundle is price inclusive , i.e. the child products are priced as zero since their price is included in the root bundle.
contextAttributes.title: IsPriceInclusive

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents whether a product attribute is price impacting or not.
contextAttributes.title: IsPriceImpacting

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the product attribute that should be considered for attribute based adjustment
contextAttributes.title: AttributeName

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents a single contributing line item or product , for a derived product.
contextAttributes.title: Contributor

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the unit price of the contributing product for a derived product.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorUnitPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the contributing product’s overall price calculated.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorTotalPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the initial price set on the contributing product for a particular derived product.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorListPrice

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents whether the contributing product is within the current transaction or outside the transaction scope.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorScope

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the source of information or data used by the contributor to determine the pricing of their product or service.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorSource

contextAttributes.description: This tag represents the formula applied on the contributing product to arrive at the derived product price.
contextAttributes.title: ContributorFormulaInput

contextAttributes.description: The tag represents the lower end of quantity of the line item/ product in the transaction above which the quantity based discounts configured for the product will be applied.
contextAttributes.title: LowerBound

contextAttributes.description: The tag represents the upper end of quantity of the line item/ product in the transaction below which the quantity based discounts configured for the product will be applied.
contextAttributes.title: UpperBound
